Package model

Class Dictionary

java.lang.Object
model.Dictionary
All Implemented Interfaces:
Iterable<Object>
public class Dictionary extends Object implements Iterable<Object>
A class representing a dictionary data structure. The dictionary stores key-value pairs and provides methods to manipulate and access the data. This class ensures that keys are unique within the dictionary and provides methods for adding, retrieving, and removing key-value pairs. Additionally, it supports iteration over keys, values, and key-value pairs.
